<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">How to Challenge in Scrabble</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Quiz · Dictionary · 3-letter words</p>

<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">The challenge is one of Scrabble's most dramatic mechanics — a high-stakes gamble that can swing a game in either direction. Knowing when to challenge (and when to let a suspicious word slide) is a skill that separates strong players from great ones.</p>

<p>In casual games, disputes are often resolved by looking up a dictionary. In tournaments, the rules are stricter — and the penalties are real. A well-timed challenge can rescue a game; a bad one can hand your opponent a free turn.</p>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">2</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Challenge systems</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">1 turn</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">NASPA penalty</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">0</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">WESPA penalty</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Challenge Rules by Format</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
    <p class="text-blue-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-2">🇺🇸 NASPA (Double Challenge)</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">If the word is invalid → player removes tiles, loses turn. If the word IS valid → challenger loses their next turn. High risk, high reward — discourages frivolous challenges.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
    <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-2">🌍 WESPA (Single Challenge)</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">If the word is invalid → player removes tiles, loses turn. If the word IS valid → play continues normally with no penalty. Encourages challenging anything suspicious.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The Challenge Window</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">⏱️ Timing Rules</p>
  <div class="space-y-3">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-amber-900/50 border border-amber-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-amber-300 font-bold">1</span>
